Date: Thu, 24 Sep 2015 11:30:21 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1125/1221] MLK-11615 ARM: dts: imx6qp-sabresd: Enable
 prefetch for the four mxcfbs

This patch enables the prefetch feature for the four mxcfbs.

Signed-off-by: Liu Ying <Ying.Liu@freescale.com>
[zou:Original patch taken from
git.freescale.com/imx/fsl-arm-yocto-bsp.git-b imx-3.14.52-1.1.0_ga]
Signed-off-by: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qp-sabresd.dts |   16 ++++++++++++++++
 1 files changed, 16 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qp-sabresd.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qp-sabresd.dts
index 8fe63a5..10a42d2 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qp-sabresd.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qp-sabresd.dts
@@ -13,6 +13,22 @@
 	model = "Freescale i.MX6 Quad Plus SABRE Smart Device Board";
 };
 
+&mxcfb1 {
+	prefetch;
+};
+
+&mxcfb2 {
+	prefetch;
+};
+
+&mxcfb3 {
+	prefetch;
+};
+
+&mxcfb4 {
+	prefetch;
+};
+
 &pre1 {
 	status = "okay";
 };
